            <h4>Vanilla, "I Vote Cupcake"</h4>
            <p>Show your red, white, and blue this midterm election with our patriotic cupcakes.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#" role="button">View details »</a></p>
          </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img class="rounded-circle" src="https://www.cupcakeroyale.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/20170925-Pumpkin-Cardamom-011-sq-220x220.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
            <h4>Pumpkin Cardamom</h4>
            <p>Cozy up this Autumn with our Pumpkin Cardamom spiced cupcakes.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#" role="button">View details »</a></p>
          </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img class="rounded-circle" src="https://www.cupcakeroyale.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/20170817-Fig-and-Honey-120-220x220.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
            <h4>Fig & Honey</h4>
            <p>Try a taste of this seasonal favorite, with locally sourced figs and honey.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#" role="button">View details »</a></p>
